form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Notice of Final Naturalization Hearing, N-4 445A

full_text: Screened by NARA, 6/1/2023 U. S. Department of Justice Immigration and Naturalization Service Notice of Final Naturalization Hearing Naturalization and Citizenship Branch 300 NORTH LOS ANGELES STREET File or A # A18 961 437 LOS ANGELES, CA 90012 Date 8/24/1987 Petition # 00697692 You are hereby notified to appear for a hearing on your petition for naturalization before a judge of the naturalization court at the DATE, TIME, AND PLACE, SHOWN BELOW. Date 9/23/1987 EDUWIGIS GONZALEY Time 12:30 PM 408 BURLINGTON AVE #216 LOSTANGELES CA 90057 Place LOS ANGELES CONVENTION CENTER 1201 SOUTH FIGUEROA STREET LOS ANGELES, CA 90015 ROOM NUMBER: HALL You must bring the following with you: - This letter, with all of the QUESTIONS ON THE REVERSE side answered in ink or on a typewriter. - Alien Registration Card. -Rentry Permit, or Refugee Travel Document. -Any Immigration documents you may have. -If the naturalization hearing is ON BEHALF OF YOUR CHILD (children), BRING your CHILD (children). If you cannot come to this hearing, return this notice immediately and state why you cannot appear. In such case, please use the return address in the extreme upper left hand corner of this letter. You will be sent another notice of hearing at a later date. Form N-445A IMPORTANT - PLEASE SEE REVERSE
